    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_eventlobby_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "如何呀？这摸起来的手感……软绵绵的吧？",
      "text_original": "どうですか？この触り心地……ふわふわでしょ？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_eventlobby_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_eventlobby_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "你是来救我的吧，老师！诶，老师你也被逮到了吗！？",
      "text_original": "助けに来てくれたんですね、先生！え、先生も捕まっちゃったんですか！？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_eventlobby_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_eventlobby_3",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "这个桌游有问题啊！怎么每次轮到我的时候都会爆炸啊！！",
      "text_original": "このボードゲームおかしいですよ！毎回私の番で爆発するんですけど！！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_eventlobby_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_eventlobby_4",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "呜呜……好挤的反省室……唉，不过这样说不定也不赖……？",
      "text_original": "うう……すし詰めの反省部屋……ま、こういうのも悪くないかも……？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_eventlobby_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_eventlogin_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "谁、谁啊！？……啊，原来是老师呀！！",
      "text_original": "だ、誰！？……あっ、先生だったんですね！！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_eventlogin_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_eventlogin_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "你来了呀，老师！我都安排好了，总之先请坐吧！",
      "text_original": "来てくれたんですね、先生！セッティングは終わってるんで、とりあえず座ってください！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_eventlogin_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_eventlogin_season_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "你来了呢！果然还是按捺不住吧？对吧！？",
      "text_original": "来ちゃいましたね！やっぱり我慢できませんでしたね？ね！？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_eventlogin_season_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_eventlogin_season_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "哼哼，就交给我吧。逃跑可是我的拿手好戏！",
      "text_original": "ふふっ、私に任せてください。脱出は私の十八番ですから！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_eventlogin_season_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_eventlogin_season_end_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "总觉得好像发生了很多事……",
      "text_original": "なんか色々あった気がするけど……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_eventlogin_season_end_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_eventlogin_season_end_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "哎，总之今晚就玩个通宵吧……！",
      "text_original": "ま、とりあえず今夜は朝まで遊び倒しちゃいましょう……！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_eventlogin_season_end_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_eventlogin_season_end_3",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "……虽然我……很想这么说……不过……捏哈。",
      "text_original": "……って、言いたいところ……なんですけど……にはっ",
