    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_lobby_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "值日吗？请稍等一下，我去拿野餐垫过来！",
      "text_original": "当番ですか？ちょっと待っててください、レジャーシート取ってきます！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_lobby_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_lobby_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "走啦走啦，去游戏厅啦！老师！",
      "text_original": "ほらほら、ゲーセン行きますよ！先生！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_lobby_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_lobby_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "老师快点过来这边！……能把灯关一下吗？",
      "text_original": "先生早くこっちきてください！……ちょっと電気消してもらっていいです？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_lobby_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_lobby_4",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "夏莱真是个好地方啊～！既没有追踪无人机，也没有防入侵的卷帘门……。",
      "text_original": "シャーレはいいところですね～！追跡用ドローンもないし、進入防止のシャッターもないし……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_lobby_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_lobby_5",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "以后别让我去反省室了，就在夏莱进行反省怎么样？可以的吧？快说可以！",
      "text_original": "反省部屋の代わりにシャーレで反省するっていうのはどうでしょう？いいですよね？いいって言ってください！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_lobby_5.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_login_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "啊！老师你来得正好～！我正准备开卡包呢！",
      "text_original": "あ！先生いいところに～！ちょうどカードパック開けるところだったんですよ！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_login_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_login_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "你好，老师！我可以吃零食吗？可以的吧？",
      "text_original": "こんにちは、先生！お菓子食べてもいいですか？いいですよね？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_login_2_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_login_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "哎呀，虽然我已经在吃了！捏哈！",
      "text_original": "ま、もう食べてるんですけどね！にははっ！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_login_2_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_memoriallobby_1_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "啊啊！？为什么偏偏在这时候放那一招啊！！",
      "text_original": "あぁっ！？なんで今その技出すんですか！！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_memoriallobby_1_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_memoriallobby_1_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "我不是说了要在我出招之后再放吗！",
      "text_original": "私の後でやってくださいっていったのに！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_memoriallobby_1_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_memoriallobby_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "是打算毁掉我完美的作战方案吗！？",
      "text_original": "完璧な作戦を崩すつもりですか！？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_memoriallobby_2_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_memoriallobby_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "我可是为了老师一大早就爬起来占位置了耶！！",
      "text_original": "先生のために朝早く起きて場所まで取ったのに！！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_memoriallobby_2_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_memoriallobby_3_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……诶？你说这是两码事？",
      "text_original": "……え？それとこれとは別の話？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_memoriallobby_3_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_memoriallobby_3_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "要是认真说的话，老师投的硬币其实更多……？",
      "text_original": "それを言うなら先生の方がコインを多く出してる……？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_memoriallobby_3_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_memoriallobby_4_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "嗯……虽然确实是这样啦，但是……。",
      "text_original": "うーん……それはそう、ですけど……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_memoriallobby_4_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_memoriallobby_4_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "唔……先休战吧！暂时休战！",
      "text_original": "むぅ……休戦にしましょう！一時休戦！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_memoriallobby_4_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_memoriallobby_5_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "没错！下次我一定会做给你看的！",
      "text_original": "そうですね！次は絶対うまくやってみせます！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_memoriallobby_5_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_memoriallobby_5_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……捏哈哈！",
      "text_original": "……にはは！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_memoriallobby_5_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_memoriallobby_5_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……捏哈哈。",
      "text_original": "……にはは。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_memoriallobby_5_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_relationship_up_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "诶？今天是什么纪念日吗？",
      "text_original": "えっ？今日って何かの記念日でしたっけ？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_relationship_up_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_relationship_up_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "老师的话，应该知道我内心的密码吧？要听听看吗？",
      "text_original": "先生は当然、私の心のパスワードなんて分かってると思いますけど？聞きます？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_relationship_up_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_relationship_up_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "这、这么照顾我真的可以吗！？没有，虽然我确实很高兴啦……！",
      "text_original": "こ、こんなにしてもらっていいんですか！？いや、すごく嬉しいですけど……！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_relationship_up_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_relationship_up_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "捏哈哈！果然还是和老师在一起的时候最开心了！",
      "text_original": "にははっ！やっぱ先生と一緒にいるときが一番楽しいですっ！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_relationship_up_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_season_birthday",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "我想要的东西……？哼～嗯？你真的想知道吗？可别后悔哦？",
      "text_original": "欲しいもの……？ふ～ん？本当に聞いちゃっていいんです？後悔、しません？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_season_birthday.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_season_birthday_player",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "生日快乐，老师！今天一起熬通宵玩个痛快！！",
      "text_original": "ハッピーバースデー！先生！今夜は徹夜で遊びまくりましょう！！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_season_birthday_player.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_season_halloween",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "居然可以穿着这身衣服在街上四处逛……！真是美好的一天啊！",
      "text_original": "こんな格好で往来を歩き回っていいなんて……！なんていい日なんでしょう！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_season_halloween.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_season_newyear_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "今天是一年的最后一天！所以不管今天做了什么，都可以留到明年再收拾！捏哈哈！",
      "text_original": "今日は一年の最後の日！だから今日は何をしても、後片付けは来年にすればいいんです！にはは！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_season_newyear_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_season_newyear_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……诶？不是最后一天？已经是新年了？这是怎么回事啊！？",
      "text_original": "……えっ？最後の日じゃない？もう年が明けてる？どういうことですか！？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_season_newyear_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0310_season_xmas",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "为了能让圣诞老人顺利过来，我把所有的安保系统都解除啦！捏哈哈！",
      "text_original": "サンタさんが無事に来れるよう、セキュリティは全部解除しておきました！にははっ！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/ch0310_season_xmas.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH0310_Title",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "Blue！Archive！",
      "text_original": "ブルー！アーカイブ！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%20%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%AA/%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3/jp/CH0310_Title.ogg"
    }
  ],
